      <description>&lt;main aria-label=&#34;Job Opportunities&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;page-title&#34; id=&#34;main-content&#34; lang=&#34;en&#34; role=&#34;main&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;layout-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hidden&#34; data-drupal-messages-fallback=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;node node--type-hwp-page node--view-mode-full&#34; lang=&#34;en&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hwp-page-title hwp-bg-light-base&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hwp-container hwp-container-px hwp-py-32&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 class=&#34;text-large&#34; id=&#34;page-title&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;span&gt;Job Opportunities&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hwp-container hwp-w-full hwp-py-32 lg:hwp-py-64 hwp-container-px lg:hwp-flex lg:hwp-gap-24&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;lg:hwp-flex-initial lg:hwp-w-[19.375rem] hwp-pb-32 hwp-shrink-0&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hwp-flex hwp-flex-col hwp-flex-1 hwp-overflow-hidden hwp-content--narrow&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hwp-mb-16 hwp-container-px&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hwp-text-block field field--name-field-hwp-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our successes result from the collective effort of a broad community. We have a lot going on, and we benefit from many different types of contributors. Our staff brings a wide range of expertise and experience to the table, as do our affiliated faculty, students, visiting scholars, post-doctoral fellows, and other academic appointees. Join us; together we will accomplish great things!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
